{"tid":857542,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【膚色正確】希里唔係黑人 Netflix公開《Witcher》真人版演員名單","createTime":"2018-10-11T07:18:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T07:24:07.000Z","uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c793d4a8031cea8aaddedd9e00a50575126b31ce","tid":857542,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:18:37.000Z","msg":"上個月真人版《Witcher》話要搵角色，製作團隊只係提一提話「可能」搵BAME ( 喺英國呢個字解類似少數族裔 ) 去演，一團眾玩家已經發左癲痴曬線，又聲討又剩，話唔要Ciri 變成黑人，搞到製作人唔敢再上Twitter ，所以有時真係唔好太輕視網上言論威力。今日Netflix 終於公開《Witcher》演員名單。<br />\n<br />\n除左之外公開，由超人演員 Henry Cavill 出演主角 白狼 傑洛特之外，今次亦公開左大量主要角色Casting。先講講搞到大家差ｄ世界大戰嘅希里Ciri 一角，將會由年僅17歲嘅少女演員Freya Allan出演，見到Ciri仲係白雪雪，仲有一對明亮嘅眼睛，大家都收曬貨。而另外Yennifer 就會由 Anya Chalotra 出演，有人就話唔係太似，不過正裝同戲入面造型就點都差少少架喇，有人亦拎左Anya 曲髮時候嘅生活照同遊戲造型做左個對比，睇落就&hellip;.都ok丫。<br />\n<br />\n其次德魯伊Mousesack 會由Adam Levy擔任、巫師薩布麗娜會係Therica Wilson-Read、辛特拉國王Esterhazy由Bjorn Hlynur Haraldsson出演等等單單睇人名大家可能唔多記得，遲ｄ大家睇劇一次過望仲好啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3igame.com/【膚色正確】希里唔係黑人-netflix公開《witcher》真人版演/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3igame.com%2F%E3%80%90%E8%86%9A%E8%89%B2%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA%E3%80%91%E5%B8%8C%E9%87%8C%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E9%BB%91%E4%BA%BA-netflix%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E3%80%8Awitcher%E3%80%8B%E7%9C%9F%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%88%E6%BC%94%2F&d=RVlam78G7dsTti9aOdoEZ49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f98194f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.3igame.com/【膚色正確】希里唔係黑人-netflix公開《witcher》真人版演/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.3igame.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Freya-Allan-for-ciri-1024x724.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3igame.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FFreya-Allan-for-ciri-1024x724.jpg&h=1cf6a334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.3igame.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/e686cb4492d7d9cf929e809da7d1.1000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3igame.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2Fe686cb4492d7d9cf929e809da7d1.1000.jpg&h=562a5910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ab736455534fa65de8ded04f009f39c8c1247f7","tid":857542,"uid":20815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:24:07.000Z","msg":"屌，演Yennifer 果個都唔係白人啦，Ciri搞唔掂就搵Yennifer 落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}